{"tid":1668444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1947年底，東北戰況危急時，蔣介石即在日記中寫道","createTime":"2019-10-22T03:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T05:58:14.000Z","uid":116471,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b7473e0b6a5819de8cd4eada7f71cb37902a54ef","tid":1668444,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:47:57.000Z","msg":"至十時禱告三次，天父許我明年耶誕節可消滅山海關以內各省之共匪，並令我不可放棄永吉、長春各要據點。可知天父之意者皆合實際與必然之理，凡遵照天意者必皆成功也。"},{"pid":"bcabc32273542d2fdab5c0d654ded73a1cb801ba","tid":1668444,"uid":116471,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"顯然上帝、天父沒有聽到蔣介石禱告，之後兵敗如山倒，每戰必敗。<br />\n<br />\n即，中國人受苦受難，乃天父之旨意也。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e677c0c0738dc4e791a6700a690136e4affd02","tid":1668444,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"長春圍城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502898330d98d05873a7bc2c24c6f095affa2730","tid":1668444,"uid":116471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11e677c0c0738dc4e791a6700a690136e4affd02","tid":1668444,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"長春圍城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:55:37.000Z","msg":"上帝的旨意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蔣公話上帝要佢死守長春。"},{"pid":"e059bd71bda74430a9a3660abe3e3db14e52e5ef","tid":1668444,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:56:11.000Z","msg":"上帝送咗杜聿明, 陳誠 比蔣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55eaefb992b6aabb7d497bf1eeb4dfe1637a2904","tid":1668444,"uid":50873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03